There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, polish
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job           | fisherman | social-worker |
| Nationality   | polish    | dutch         |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing  |
| Transport   | ship  | motorbike |

